Takius-san?

84
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,590
Takius-kun... Takius-kun...

85
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:12,560
Sensei!

86
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:16,530
Musíš to zastavit, Takius-kun. 

87
